{"tid":2231531,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣加完雪種一個月又漏","createTime":"2020-10-05T17:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:48:58.000Z","uid":183997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"26a9309f7b7bd0cf87bde177d06a475e78c4c5c9","tid":2231531,"uid":183997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟架07年豐田QNC21 bB，上個月因為架車唔凍去整開車房加爆雪種，到呢個禮拜發現架車又開始唔凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日開到最凍只不過吹微涼風...跟住就駛去車房，去到再幫我加爆雪種...架車就凍翻...<br />\n咁應該係壞<span class=\"x-large\">凍Coli</span>定<span class=\"x-large\">冷氣泵</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f9d3d675137f0ce062dd090fb471b7c35961bd","tid":2231531,"uid":280329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:15:37.000Z","msg":"高低壓喉 冷COLI 都有機會<br />\n如果真係漏既話 睇下雪總條路邊到有油漏"},{"pid":"b2243a669bd21e7de04dc39026f09ac630386762","tid":2231531,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"喉漏唔得嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喉漏機會比較多<br />\n你摸到嘅地方就摸下<br />\n由其個沙樽<br />\n再唔係打轉營光濟<br />\n一照就知邊度漏"},{"pid":"cb64d9c4074c2b049f3e001023c16ba270196861","tid":2231531,"uid":179114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"漏雪種壞乜鳩<br />\n入完一個星期就漏到唔凍即係大漏<br />\n咁都搵唔到叫間車房食屎啦"},{"pid":"cdd4adb9c10091a28e5be0821531925083d85739","tid":2231531,"uid":244105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"同冷氣機一樣?<br />\n漏雪種即係有洩漏 加翻滿都係會漏<br />\n要成個換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1747c92d89779da6f95e63defcf352614a1962","tid":2231531,"uid":183997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2243a669bd21e7de04dc39026f09ac630386762","tid":2231531,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"喉漏唔得嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喉漏機會比較多<br />\n你摸到嘅地方就摸下<br />\n由其個沙樽<br />\n再唔係打轉營光濟<br />\n一照就知邊度漏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"買枝先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該曬巴打，聽日自己去摸下先"},{"pid":"29727a104b6fc2f278055ef85a0c36642d8be884","tid":2231531,"uid":183997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cb64d9c4074c2b049f3e001023c16ba270196861","tid":2231531,"uid":179114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"漏雪種壞乜鳩<br />\n入完一個星期就漏到唔凍即係大漏<br />\n咁都搵唔到叫間車房食屎啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"佢上次淨係幫我整個冷氣都整左我八日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後話加翻雪種就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161973b08738ed270d494820735722dec41a245b","tid":2231531,"uid":28244,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"每日停車睇下高低壓氣雪種喉 照下睇下有冇油 摸下佢 <br />\n有就清潔好 第二日/再揸 揸完再睇多次<br />\n另外就係散熱網 你BB唔拆泵把睇唔哂成隻 <br />\n凍coil漏 咁既漏速你車籠臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下下收你幾舊打雪種 唔幫你跟 佢發仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ba9d20927a1a552b58f5f0616d86426d4208a8","tid":2231531,"uid":77453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:34:57.000Z","msg":"多數D 接口位 凍coil 漏 因成件野 都係薄"},{"pid":"a9c57f1d87575163d7f4eca3d0f5014c6f88e58d","tid":2231531,"uid":183997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161973b08738ed270d494820735722dec41a245b","tid":2231531,"uid":28244,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"每日停車睇下高低壓氣雪種喉 照下睇下有冇油 摸下佢 <br />\n有就清潔好 第二日/再揸 揸完再睇多次<br />\n另外就係散熱網 你BB唔拆泵把睇唔哂成隻 <br />\n凍coil漏 咁既漏速你車籠臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/fa